OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,FA mother of a young man who died
OL,7,Fduring the coronavirus pandemic has
OL,8,Ftold UTV of the devastating moment her
OL,9,Fson died.
OL,11,FBriege McEvoy spoke to UTV's current
OL,12,Faffairs programme Up Close which
OL,13,Fexamined the recent visit of the UK
OL,14,FCovid Inquiry to Belfast.
OL,16,FShe hit out at some of the decisions
OL,17,Fmade during the pandemic, saying she
OL,18,Fbelieved they "cost lives".
