OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,FBriege said her son was prescribed
OL,7,Fsteroids after contracting Covid, but
OL,8,Fhis condition never improved. Without
OL,9,Fbeing admitted to hospital, Conor died
OL,10,Fat home with his mum.
OL,12,F"Conor was sitting at the end of the
OL,13,Fbed drinking a glass of water, and the
OL,14,Fnext thing his breathing went really
OL,15,Freally fast," she said.
OL,17,F"So I dialed 999 and I heard Conor
OL,18,Fshout, 'are you there mum?' and I ran
OL,19,Fupstairs into his room... and he
OL,20,Flooked at me and said, 'mum'.
