OL,6,F"And that was it, he dropped to the
OL,7,Ffloor. He was gone."
OL,9,FThe examines the evidence given at the
OL,10,Frecent Covid inquiry. Taking a deep
OL,11,Fdive into the three-week long Covid
OL,12,FInquiry, analysing the shocking
OL,13,Frevelations uncovered and hearing from
OL,14,Fthe families who lost loved ones to
OL,15,FCovid.
OL,17,FAfter losing her husband to Covid in
OL,18,F2021, Julie McMurray said she was
OL,19,Fdetermined he would not become a
OL,20,Fstatistic.
