OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,FJulie's husband Robert had been
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with early onset dementia.
OL,8,FHe tested positive with Covid after an
OL,9,Foperation in hospital during his
OL,10,Frecovery. Julie would visit him every
OL,11,Fday, until lockdown restrictions were
OL,12,Fimposed.
OL,14,FConfused and distressed without seeing
OL,15,Fhis family, Roberts health
OL,16,Fdeteriorated.
OL,18,FJulie said he got confused and would
OL,19,Fask her, "Why have you left me?"
