OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,F"I made a promise to look after him,"
OL,7,Fshe told UTV, "I told him we would get
OL,8,Fthrough it.
OL,10,FWhen Julie finally got to see Robert
OL,11,Fhis condition has deteriorated.
OL,13,F"He could barely squeeze my hand....
OL,14,Fit was too late."
OL,16,FThe son of a fit and healthy 90 year-
OL,17,Fold woman spoke to UTV about receiving
OL,18,Fphone calls from doctors where they
OL,19,Fwould assess his mum's chances of
OL,20,Freceiving life-changing treatment
OL,21,Fbased on her age and ability.
