OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,FAsking why they were questioning him
OL,7,Fon his mum's health doctors said they
OL,8,Fhad to make decisions as oxygen
OL,9,Fsupplies were running low.
OL,11,FShe died in hospital during the second
OL,12,Fwave of Covid.
OL,14,F"And I thought, how are we still
OL,15,Frunning out of stuff in the second
OL,16,Fwave? A year later?," Robert told UTV.
