OL,3,C'They cost lives': Heartbroken mum
OL,4,Crecalls son's death during pandemic
OL,6,F"A lot of people talk about people
OL,7,Fdying in the nursing homes, which is
OL,8,Fquite right. But a lot of people died
OL,9,Fin hospital and my mother was one of
OL,10,Fthem and this should never have went
OL,11,Fthis far.J"The inquiry showed up a lot
OL,12,Fof failings in our government."
OL,14,FThe programme also discussed the Covid
OL,15,FInquiry sessions with Brenda Doherty
OL,16,FwhoJrepresents bereaved families,
OL,17,Fformer civil servant Ann Watt, Belfast
OL,18,FTelegraph journalist and commentator
OL,19,FSam McBride as well as from Deborah
OL,20,FMcAleese and UTV's Political Editor
OL,21,FTracey Magee.
